{"tid":1397604,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[我今次唔攬炒]和理非可以點樣係重大戰役幫前線？以後一齊接放學啦！！","createTime":"2019-08-02T14:00:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-03T04:08:07.000Z","uid":89974,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"14fed594479fe58d92d8a05c62e11cdafc7c185a","tid":1397604,"uid":89974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T14:00:40.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">前言：</span></span><br />\n次次大會見到前線亡命抵抗，你想除咗食花生涼冷氣之外都出一分力？見到好多家長有車接仔女放學，好想幫手救人？<br />\n<strong>三十歲人都仲要依賴交通工具嘅你地都得架</strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />大家一齊落去地鐵站食花生！！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">目標：</span></span><br />\n保障每一個放學仔女既安全<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n增加士氣，話俾前線聽好多人撐佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">行動綱領：</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: navy;\">如果你有發開夢，當日係附近地鐵站：<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">唔好咁早撤退！11點前都留係站內做支援！你一個<strong>普通人</strong>食完飯途經地鐵站係唔會俾人拉架！</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">唔好咁早撤退！11點前都留係站內做支援！你一個<strong>普通人</strong>食完飯途經地鐵站係唔會俾人拉架！</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">唔好咁早撤退！11點前都留係站內做支援！你一個<strong>普通人</strong>食完飯途經地鐵站係唔會俾人拉架！</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: navy;\">如果你個日要番屋企食飯，落唔到場<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">每逢有大型活動，夜晚9-12點落去最近你屋企嘅地鐵站涼冷氣散步睇直播<strong>放下狗</strong><br />\n每逢有大型活動，夜晚9-12點落去最近你屋企嘅地鐵站涼冷氣散步睇直播<strong>放下狗</strong><br />\n每逢有大型活動，夜晚9-12點落去最近你屋企嘅地鐵站涼冷氣散步睇直播<strong>放下狗</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">Q&amp;A</span></span><br />\n1. 接放學著乜好？<br />\n<strong> 街坊裝</strong>又得，<strong>黑色衫</strong>又得，香港地好易病記住帶<strong>口罩</strong>，夏天成日打風攞定<strong>直遮</strong><br />\n<br />\n2. 要查我身份證喎，點算？<br />\n問佢攞委任證先，記住你人愈多愈安全，班狗係唔會兇你<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EHCJ02r.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEHCJ02r.jpg&h=8271b768&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n重複多幾次：<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">唔駛早撤退！多落街跑步<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔駛早撤退！多落街跑步<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔駛早撤退！多落街跑步<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n我會每次集會前將會重開一次呢個POST提醒大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"055b593ffdaa6787f02c9fae14cf0eac5fe4ba73","tid":1397604,"uid":89974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T14:00:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7eed62033eb39d450b4e867b947391908a5e18ff","tid":1397604,"uid":89974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T14:00:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0b498401607697cf0427eee022e5c98af8c640c","tid":1397604,"uid":89974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T14:01:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50beee6b0b27f2893284af6015bacb682087f8f2","tid":1397604,"uid":89974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T14:01:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f83a7d6ed14808fcaceaaa456489a6aa3ad31db","tid":1397604,"uid":89974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T14:01:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c38633fdb44b51b5e04e78f016dc